{"tid":1492214,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"停工1個月！Mina「突現身TWICE私下聚餐」網一看哭了：OMG","createTime":"2019-08-20T17:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T12:44:33.000Z","uid":74065,"like":18,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ccdeac240a719f3db001dd004ef6537a39e4699c","tid":1492214,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:27:24.000Z","msg":"南韓女團TWICE的日本籍成員Mina日前傳出罹患舞台恐慌症，並宣布全面中止活動，如今已經休息1個月，TWICE官方Instagram20日突然PO出一系列「8人合照」，畫面中還可以看到Mina的身影，讓大票粉絲興奮直呼：「終於看到Mina了」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4318/d4318204.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4318%2Fd4318204.jpg&h=b9068ea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Mina患上舞台恐慌症，目前仍在休息中。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／TWICE）<br />\n<br />\nTWICE官方Instagram20日更新近況，突然PO出8個成員的合照，只見畫面中，成員們坐在一塊聚餐，看起來溫馨又歡樂，不過在大合照中，卻唯獨缺少娜璉，被猜測照片應是由她掌鏡，而正在休養的Mina也出現在照片中，只見她簡單地穿著黑色小背心入鏡，看起來氣色非常好。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4318/4318206.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4318%2F4318206.jpg&h=deeaab4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4318/4318207.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4318%2F4318207.jpg&h=1240abd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然有部分網友指出這似乎不是近期所拍攝的照片，但TWICE8人久違的合照，還是讓粉絲相當感動，紛紛開心直呼：「終於看到Mina了」、「想妳了，要好好恢復啊」、「都要好好的啊！期待妳們8人回歸」、「OMG！Mina」、「好開心看到Mina沒事」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4318/4318209.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4318%2F4318209.jpg&h=07cab9e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼Mina出現在TWICE合照。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／TWICE）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4318/4318208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4318%2F4318208.jpg&h=cb60b97f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事實上，Mina爆出恐慌症後，她回到家鄉日本進行休養，她8月1日在媽媽的陪同下突然返韓，被猜測是否要回歸團隊，對此，經紀公司JYP娛樂表示：「Mina在1日抵達韓國將和媽媽一起度過，就如過去所說的，Mina為了痊癒正在靜養休息，未來行程計畫並不會有變動。」"},{"pid":"fcab92da2a525e775f943585626f57627a8fbce6","tid":1492214,"uid":240447,"like":57,"dislike":9,"score":48,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"滿月酒"},{"pid":"f89a462bbd7eebb8dadf8dd4baa148cb593d3008","tid":1492214,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fcab92da2a525e775f943585626f57627a8fbce6","tid":1492214,"uid":240447,"like":57,"dislike":9,"score":48,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"滿月酒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884707826d12b19076e61d5f41c4f01238c3dd07","tid":1492214,"uid":251836,"like":40,"dislike":8,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:30:33.000Z","msg":"咁快安完胎"},{"pid":"38d0c623f67d54bec3dcc56309c57a9455d8fbdc","tid":1492214,"uid":138138,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:33:38.000Z","msg":"就如過去所說的，Mina為了痊癒正在靜養休息"},{"pid":"fccffe02320f551cb450a587b9cb58dea295a0a0","tid":1492214,"uid":240447,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"f89a462bbd7eebb8dadf8dd4baa148cb593d3008","tid":1492214,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fcab92da2a525e775f943585626f57627a8fbce6","tid":1492214,"uid":240447,"like":57,"dislike":9,"score":48,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"滿月酒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:35:07.000Z","msg":"I mean 停工滿月啫<br />\n唔好諗多"},{"pid":"64b512799a1cfd3c889cbdeab5bf2c8f1438d90e","tid":1492214,"uid":190066,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:47:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7228243e60e25bb94478250b4d5a538f16bd6ea6","tid":1492214,"uid":29